models.abstract: American radio broadcaster Paul Harvey has died at the age of 90.
models.headline: Broadcaster Paul Harvey dies at age 90

models.abstract: A miscommunication between the Tulsa Police Department in Oklahoma, US and a Tulsa TV reporter has led to a man dressed as "Pedobear" at the San Diego Comic Con being erroneously labeled as a "registered sex offender."
models.headline: Tulsa media erroneously reports San Diego Comic Con Pedobear was 'registered sex offender'
